30T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"漫畫好似未死,,,<br />\n<br />\n不過每年都要訓一訓...*一訓就唔知幾時醒, 唔訓又會死*<br />\n<br />\nThe Odinsleep, also known as the Forever Sleep - is a state of deep sleep where Odin (and after him, Thor) recharges the Odin-Force and is left as vulnerable as a mortal. The duration of the Odinsleep varies from time to time; sometimes it's a single night while other occasions are for more than a week. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Odin_Borson_(Earth-616)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmarvel.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FOdin_Borson_%28Earth-616%29&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=392cf954\" target=\"_blank\">https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Odin_Borson_(Earth-616)</a>"}]}